modularrouters.guiText.popup.activator.e:
§a§nEntity Mode§r

Define which nearby (within 3 blocks) entity to target each time the module runs: 
- The closest entity; 
- An entity picked at random; 
- Round-robin through all in-range entities.

modularrouters.guiText.popup.activator.l:
§a§nLook Direction§r

When right-clicking, the router can: 
- Face level, targeting a block directly in the module's direction, up to 4 blocks away; 
- Look upward, targeting the block directly above the block in the module's direction; 
- Look downward, targeting the block directly below the block in the module's direction.

modularrouters.guiText.popup.detector.we:
§a§nRedstone Signal Strength§r

- A §oweak§r redstone signal will power the adjacent block only; 
- A §ostrong§r redstone signal will power the adjacent block and blocks adjacent to that block (like a vanilla Repeater).
